SECTION 3 — INTENDED USE

PagedIn is built for:
  • Individuals creating personal resume websites
  • Businesses creating free landing pages and brand one-pagers
  • Educational and portfolio purposes

It is not intended for, and must not be used for:
  • Generating spam, phishing pages, or fraudulent content
  • Impersonating real individuals or organizations
  • Any unlawful purpose under applicable law

